Title: Remember Nothing
Plot: When Xena defends the Fates's temple, they give her the gift of changing the past: her brother Lyceus never died and she never became the warrior princess...but that also means she never met Gabrielle.
Director: Anson Williams, Steven L. Sears, Chris Manheim
GuestStars: Aaron Devitt, Robert Harte, Stephen Tozer, Rebecca Kpacka, Micaela Daniel, Elizabeth Pendergrast, Slade Leef, Mark Ferguson
